msgstr "Account type (student / teacher)"

#: templates/legal/privacy.html:33
msgid "Для учителей: образование, опыт, расписание, сертификаты, видео-визитка"
msgstr ""
"For teachers: education, experience, schedule, certificates, intro video"

#: templates/legal/privacy.html:35
msgid "Автоматически при использовании"
msgstr "Automatically as you use the service"

#: templates/legal/privacy.html:37
